def maximumUniqueSubarray(nums):
    start = end = 1
    numSet = set()
    maxScore = currScore = 0
    while end < len(nums):
        if nums[end] not in numSet:
            numSet.add(nums[end])
            currScore += nums[end]
            maxScore = max(maxScore, currScore)
            end += 1
        else:
            numSet.remove(nums[start])
            currScore -= nums[start]
            start += 1
    return maxScore
